author: @ejga
text:
Holy crap I only now get to know this precious gem exists. It's crazy to see someone as extremely talented and gorgeous as Momo just fangirling around over a teammate, she's so humble and loving and has the skill to make us see Nayeon even more perfect than she usually is, as if it was already not enough.

I was an already grownass dude which was totally unaware of the kpop scene until ICSM era, when the algorithm somehow introduced this group to me and I immediately got wrecked by Nayeon and eventually by all of them and got to know their precious bond and amazing journey.

Nowadays I can't help myself but to be more and more infatuated by this group. I'm not even into kpop as a whole, Twice is just this rare little side of my life, a happy place where I recieve all the serotonin I need to keep me alive. 

Also, sleepy Nayeon is now living rent free in my mind as the most beautiful thing in the entire universe.
